this program opens and reads the following three data files:
customers
orders
products

all data in these files are in CSV data format


Requirements:

After every row is read the following information must be displayed:

Every customer.
Output format: Customer: <name>, <address>
Every product.
Output format: Product: <name>, <price>
Total amount ordered per product.
Output format: <product name> amount: <amount>
Total money spent per product.
Output format: <product name> gross income: <amount>
Total money spent per customer.
Output format: <name> money spent: <amount>